.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: chestnut, orange, grey, brown, emerald
Nationality: russian, argentine, dutch, brazilian, indonesian
Cigar: dunhill, emeraldmaster, oliveros, baccarat, game
Beverage: hot-chocolate, mirinda, lemonade, juice, iced-tea
Pet: lizard, turtle, fish, cat, rabbit

1. Nationality:russian == Color:chestnut
2. Nationality:argentine == Pet:lizard
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate == Color:orange
4. Nationality:dutch == Beverage:mirinda
5. Color:orange is to the right of Color:grey
6. Cigar:dunhill == Pet:rabbit
7. Cigar:emeraldmaster == Color:brown
8. Beverage:lemonade is in the middle
9. Nationality:brazilian is on the far left
10. Cigar:oliveros is on the left or right of Pet:turtle
11. Cigar:emeraldmaster is to the left or right of Pet:cat
12. Cigar:baccarat == Beverage:juice
13. Nationality:indonesian == Cigar:game
14. Nationality:brazilian is to the left or right of Color:emerald

